                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Hm.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Mendel Herskovitz</b>
                    <p class="utterance">...and that person...he was stretched out on a bench...</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
