                    <p class="utterance">...and he was administered...it depended...twenty-five...hundred...</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Hm.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Mendel Herskovitz</b>
                    <p class="utterance">One did withstand it, and another did not withstand it.</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
