                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Hm. [an interrupted word].</p>
                                                                                                <b>Mendel Herskovitz</b>
                    <p class="utterance">And one did withstand it...It went by...One it didn&#39;t hurt...</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Hm.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Mendel Herskovitz</b>
                    <p class="utterance">...especially...</p>
                                                                                                <b>David Boder</b>
                    <p class="utterance">Hm.</p>
                                                                                                <b>Mendel Herskovitz</b>
